import "experimental"

startlist = from(bucket: "jmeter")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "events" and r["_value"]=~/.*started.*/)
  |> group(columns: ["_start"])
  |> keep(columns:["testRun","_time"])

  


FinalOutput = ["_field", "_time", "_value"]

metrics = from(bucket: "jmeter")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "jmeter" and r["transaction"] == "all")



out4 = metrics |> filter(fn: (r) =>  r["_field"] == "avg" and r["statut"] == "all")
  |> mean()
  |> toInt()
  |> group(columns: ["_start"])
  |> keep(columns:["_time","testRun","_value","application"])



out5 = metrics |> filter(fn: (r) =>  r["_field"] == "pct99.0" and r["statut"] == "all")
  |> mean()
    |> toInt()
    |> group(columns: ["_start"])
  |> keep(columns:["_time","testRun","_value","application"])


out6 = metrics |> filter(fn: (r) =>  r["_field"] == "avg" and r["statut"] == "all")
  |> count()
    |> group(columns: ["_start"])
  |> keep(columns:["_time","testRun","_value","application"])

count1 = metrics |> filter(fn: (r) => r["statut"] == "all" and  r["_field"] == "count")
 |> sum()
   |> group(columns: ["_start"])
  |> keep(columns:["_time","testRun","_value","application"])


error1 = metrics |> filter(fn: (r) => r["statut"] == "all" and r["_field"] == "countError")
 |> sum()
   |> group(columns: ["_start"])
  |> keep(columns:["_time","testRun","_value","application"])

errors = join(
  tables: {count1:count1, error1:error1},
  on: ["testRun"]
)
    |> map(fn: (r) => ({
      errors: r._value_error1 / r._value_count1,
      testRun: r.testRun,
      application: r.application
    })
  )


first = join(tables:{out4:out4, out5:out5}, on:["testRun"])
|> map(fn: (r) => ({
      avg: r._value_out4 ,
      pct: r._value_out5,
      testRun: r.testRun,
      application: r.application
    })
  )

second = join(tables:{out6:out6, errors:errors}, on:["testRun"])
 |> map(fn: (r) => ({
      time_spent: r._value*5 ,
      errors: r.errors,
      testRun: r.testRun,
      application: r.application
    })
  )

third = join(tables:{first:first, second:second}, on:["testRun"])



fourth = join(tables:{startlist:startlist, third:third}, on:["testRun"])
 |> map(fn: (r) => ({
      time_spent: r.time_spent,
      errors: r.errors,
      testRun: r.testRun,
      avg: r.avg,
      pct: r.pct,
      application: r.application,
      time_start: int (v:uint(v:r._time)) / 1000000,
      time_end: int (v:uint(v:experimental.addDuration(       
        d: duration(v: r.time_spent*1000000000),
        to: r._time,
    )))/1000000
    })
  )
|> sort(columns:["time_start"], desc : true)
|> yield()

a = from(bucket: "jmeter")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "jmeter" and r["application"] == "${project}" and r["testRun"]== "${run}" )

out1 = a |> filter(fn: (r) =>  (r["_field"] == "count" or r["_field"] == "countError") and r["statut"] == "all")
  |> sum()
  |> group(columns: ["_field", "transaction"])

out2 = a |> filter(fn: (r) =>  (r["_field"] != "count" and  r["_field"] != "countError") and r["statut"] == "all")
  |> group(columns: ["_field","transaction"])
  |> mean(column: "_value")
  |> group()

out3 = a |> filter(fn: (r) =>  r["_field"] == "count" and r["statut"] == "ko")
  |> sum()
  |> group(columns: ["_field", "transaction"])
  |> set(key: "_field", value: "error")

out4 = a |> filter(fn: (r) =>  r["_field"] == "count" and r["statut"] == "all")
  |> map(fn: (r) => ({
    r with
    _value: float(v: r._value) / 5.0
  })
)
  |> top(n:15)
  |> quantile(q: 0.5, method: "exact_selector")
  |> group(columns: ["_field", "transaction"])
  |> set(key: "_field", value: "rps")

output = union (tables: [out1,out2, out3,out4]) 
 |> group()
 |> pivot(
    rowKey:["transaction"],
    columnKey: ["_field"],
    valueColumn: "_value"
  )
 |> yield()

total = join(tables: {c:c, b:b},
  on: ["_time","transaction"])
     |> group(columns: ["_time","transaction"])
     |> reduce(fn: (r, accumulator) => ({
      tolerance_count: if r._value_c<${apdex}/3 then accumulator.tolerance_count + r._value_b

      untolerance_count: if r._value_c>${apdex}/3 and r._value_c<${apdex} then accumulator.untolerance_count + r._value_b
      else accumulator.untolerance_count,
      total: accumulator.total + r._value_b,
    }),
    identity: {tolerance_count: 0.0, untolerance_count: 0.0, total: 0.0}
  )
    |> group(columns: ["transaction"])
